title: Stunning NEW Community!
posting_body: ['Listing #2022', 'Welcome home to this casual yet elegant, vibrant yet relaxed apartment community!', 'You will love the perfect blend of trendy and charming.', 'You are sure to find this to be the right space that’s perfectly suited to your personality!', 'Custom designed floor plans', 'Stainless steel GE appliance package', 'GE Energy Star front load full-size washer and dryer', 'Stunning kitchen with 42” custom cabinets featuring luna pearl granite countertops, under-mount sink, & designer ceramic tile backsplash', '9-foot ceilings with fans', 'Designer wood-style plank flooring', 'Upscale carpet in bedroom suites', 'Spacious en-suite master bath with luna pearl granite countertops, modern tile bath, & shower surrounds', 'Wi-Fi programmable thermostats', 'Wood style 2” blinds', 'Walk-in closets', 'USB outlets', 'Call today to schedule your free tour!', 'I have access to over 1000 apartment listing in all areas in and around the beautiful Austin, Texas!', 'Should this listing not fit exactly what you are looking for, I am happy to help you find your next home!', 'Matt Davidson - Licensed Agent', 'Dash Apartment Locating', 'Dash Realty', 'show contact info', 'Listing #2022']
